plot: Anibal, Mudok, Félix and M-30 are ex-members of a US Commando unit in the Vietnam War. Wanted by the police all over the world, they survive as a soldiers of fortune. This time, they are going to help his old friend in his fight against another old friend in NAM: Sergeant Mulligan.   Written by  Luis Capote
title: El Equipo Aahhgg
